Package: fungwasStage2
Title: Flexible Functional GWAS via RIF Quantile Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Description: RIF-based quantile GWAS with parametric mapping. Stage 2 of the 
    FungWas pipeline: maps tau-level SNP effects into distributional parameters
    (means, variances, mixture components) with proper standard error estimation.
